Package Models

Class MovieGoer

java.lang.Object
Models.User
Models.MovieGoer
public class MovieGoer extends User
Represents a MovieGoer in our application. This is for MovieGoers that are registered in our application. Subclass of the base User class. This class inherits the following attributes from the base User class: username password age
